itle="Network Management Research Group" href="nmrg">NMRG</a></li> <li><a title="Routing Research Group" href="rrg">RRG</a></li> <li><a title="Scalable Adaptive Multicast Research Group" href="samrg">SAMRG</a></li> <li><a title="Software-Defined Networking Research Group" href="sdnrg">SDNRG</a></li> </ul> <h2>Other Activities</h2> <ul> <li> <a href='anrp'>Applied Networking Research Prize</a> </li> </ul> <h2>Internet Research Steering Group</h2> <ul> <li> <a href='chair'>IRTF Chair</a> </li> </ul> <ul> <li> <a href='irsg'>IRSG Members</a> </li> </ul> <h2>IPR</h2> <ul> <li> <a href='ipr'>Intellectual Property Rights</a> </li> </ul> <h2>Sponsors</h2> <ul> <li> <a href='http://ietf.org/'> <img alt='Internet Engineering Task Force (IETF)' height='53' src='img/ietf.png' width='100'> </a> </li> <li> <a href='http://isoc.org/'> <img alt='Internet Society (ISOC)' height='40' src='img/isoc.png' width='100'> </a> </li> </ul> </div> <div class='main'> <a id='content'></a> <div class='rightbar'> <h2>Chair</h2> <p> The <a href="irsg">IRSG</a> is chaired by the <a href="chair">IRTF Chair</a>, <a href='http://eggert.org/'>Lars Eggert</a> (<a href="mailto:irtf-chair@irtf.org">irtf-chair@irtf.org</a>). </p> <h2>Mailing Lists</h2> <p> <a href='/mailman/listinfo/irsg'>irsg@irtf.org</a> is the private discussion list of the <a href="irsg">IRSG</a>. </p> <h2>Wiki</h2> <p> The main <a href='http://trac.tools.ietf.org/group/irtf/trac/wiki'>IRTF wiki</a> is used by the <a href="irsg">IRSG</a> to manage its activities. </p> </div> <p>The <a href="./">IRTF</a> is managed by the <a href="chair">IRTF Chair</a> in consultation with the Internet Research Steering Group (<a href="irsg">IRSG</a>). The <a href="irsg">IRSG</a> membership includes the <a href="chair">IRTF Chair</a>, the chairs of the various <a href="groups">Research Groups</a> and other individuals (&#8220;members at large&#8221;) from the research or <a href="http://ietf.org/">IETF</a> communities.</p> <p><a href="irsg">IRSG</a> members at large are chosen by the <a href="chair">IRTF Chair</a> in consultation with the rest of the <a href="irsg">IRSG</a> and on approval by the <a href="https://iab.org/">IAB</a>.</p> <p>In addition to managing the <a href="groups">Research Groups</a>, the <a href="irsg">IRSG</a> may from time to time hold topical workshops focusing on research areas of importance to the evolution of the Internet, or more general workshops to, for example, discuss research priorities from an Internet perspective.</p> <p>The <a href="irsg">IRSG</a> also reviews and approves documents published as part of the <a href="./">IRTF</a> Document Stream (<a href="http://wiki.tools.ietf.org/html/rfc5743">RFC 5743</a>).</p> <p> The current <a href="irsg">IRSG</a> membership includes the <a href="chair">IRTF Chair</a>, 18 Research Group Chairs and 6 At-Large Members: </p> <ul> <li><a href="http://eggert.org/">Lars Eggert</a> (<a href="mailto:irtf-chair@irtf.org">irtf-chair@irtf.org</a>), <a href="chair">IRTF Chair</a></li> <li><a href="http://www.icir.org/mallman/">Mark Allman</a> (<a href="mailto:mallman@icir.org">mallman@icir.org</a>), At-Large Member</li> <li><a href="http://linkedin.com/in/spencerdawkins">Spencer Dawkins</a> (<a href="mailto:spencer@wonderhamster.org">spencer@wonderhamster.org</a>), At-Large Member</li> <li><a href="http://linkedin.com/in/aaronfalk">Aaron Falk</a> (<a href="mailto:aaron.falk@gmail.com">aaron.falk@gmail.com</a>), At-Large Member</li> <li><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/russ-housley/0/69/419">Russ Housley</a> (<a href="mailto:housley@vigilsec.com">housley@vigilsec.com</a>), At-Large Member</li> <li><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/eliot-lear/0/81/b0a">Eliot Lear</a> (<a href="mailto:lear@cisco.com">lear@cisco.com</a>), At-Large Member</li> <li><a href="http://www.net-glyph.org/lixing/">Xing Li</a> (<a href="mailto:xing@cernet.edu.cn">xing@cernet.edu.cn</a>), At-Large Member</li> <li>Kevin Igoe (<a href="mailto:kmigoe@nsa.gov">kmigoe@nsa.gov</a>), <a title="Crypto Forum Research Group" href="cfrg">CFRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://mindspring.com/~dmcgrew/dam.htm">David McGrew</a> (<a href="mailto:mcgrew@cisco.com">mcgrew@cisco.com</a>), <a title="Crypto Forum Research Group" href="cfrg">CFRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://kfall.net/ucbpage/">Kevin Fall</a> (<a href="mailto:kfall@acm.org">kfall@acm.org</a>), <a title="Delay-Tolerant Networking Research Group" href="dtnrg">DTNRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="https://cs.tcd.ie/Stephen.Farrell/">Stephen Farrell</a> (<a href="mailto:stephen.farrell@cs.tcd.ie">stephen.farrell@cs.tcd.ie</a>), <a title="Delay-Tolerant Networking Research Group" href="dtnrg">DTNRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://www.netlab.tkk.fi/~jo/">Jörg Ott</a> (<a href="mailto:jo@netlab.tkk.fi">jo@netlab.tkk.fi</a>), <a title="Delay-Tolerant Networking Research Group" href="dtnrg">DTNRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://www.telecom-bretagne.eu/studies/msc/professors/ros.php">David Ros</a> (<a href="mailto:david.ros@telecom-bretagne.eu">david.ros@telecom-bretagne.eu</a>), <a title="Internet Congestion Control Research Group" href="iccrg">ICCRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://heim.ifi.uio.no/michawe/">Michael Welzl</a> (<a href="mailto:michawe@ifi.uio.no">michawe@ifi.uio.no</a>), <a title="Internet Congestion Control Research Group" href="iccrg">ICCRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://dirk-kutscher.info/">Dirk Kutscher</a> (<a href="mailto:dirk.kutscher@neclab.eu">dirk.kutscher@neclab.eu</a>), <a title="Information-Centric Networking Research Group" href="icnrg">ICNRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/b%3Frje-ohlman/0/270/283">Börje Ohlman</a> (<a href="mailto:borje.ohlman@ericsson.com">borje.ohlman@ericsson.com</a>), <a title="Information-Centric Networking Research Group" href="icnrg">ICNRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/david-oran/0/b7/7b4">Dave Oran</a> (<a href="mailto:oran@cisco.com">oran@cisco.com</a>), <a title="Information-Centric Networking Research Group" href="icnrg">ICNRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://linkedin.com/in/mbehringer">Michael Behringer</a> (<a href="mailto:mbehring@cisco.com">mbehring@cisco.com</a>), <a title="Network Complexity Research Group" href="ncrg">NCRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://www.1-4-5.net/~dmm/vita.html">David Meyer</a> (<a href="mailto:dmm@1-4-5.net">dmm@1-4-5.net</a>), <a title="Network Complexity Research Group" href="ncrg">NCRG</a> &amp; <a title="Software-Defined Networking Research Group" href="sdnrg">SDNRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://www.loria.fr/~festor/Site/Welcome.html">Olivier Festor</a> (<a href="mailto:olivier.festor@inria.fr">olivier.festor@inria.fr</a>), <a title="Network Management Research Group" href="nmrg">NMRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://inf.ufrgs.br/~granville/">Lisandro Granville</a> (<a href="mailto:granville@inf.ufrgs.br">granville@inf.ufrgs.br</a>), <a title="Network Management Research Group" href="nmrg">NMRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://linkedin.com/pub/tony-li/0/130/2a9">Tony Li</a> (<a href="mailto:tony.li@tony.li">tony.li@tony.li</a>), <a title="Routing Research Group" href="rrg">RRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://samrg.org/buford/index.html">John Buford</a> (<a href="mailto:buford@samrg.org">buford@samrg.org</a>), <a title="Scalable Adaptive Multicast Research Group" href="samrg">SAMRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://users.informatik.haw-hamburg.de/~schmidt/">Thomas Schmidt</a> (<a href="mailto:schmidt@informatik.haw-hamburg.de">schmidt@informatik.haw-hamburg.de</a>), <a title="Scalable Adaptive Multicast Research Group" href="samrg">SAMRG</a> Chair</li> <li><a href="http://www.cc.gatech.edu/~feamster/">Nick Feamster</a> (<a href="mailto:feamster@cc.gatech.edu">feamster@cc.gatech.edu</a>), <a title="Software-Defined Networking Research Group" href="sdnrg">SDNRG</a> Chair</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class='layout_footer'></div> </div> <div class='footer noprint'> <div class='left'> <div cl